org.mixare.lib.marker.draw

Class ParcelableProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mixare.lib.marker.draw.ParcelableProperty

  • public class ParcelableProperty
extends java.lang.Object
    A draw property which contains a parcelable object with its classname so it can be loaded. This class should be used, when a plugin wants to send a 'unknown' parcelable object to the core This is needed because the classname of a parcel should be known before the core can convert that into an object.
    Author:
    A. Egal
